# Copy to .env and fill in your key.
# Get a key at https://console.cloud.google.com/
#
# Enable these APIs on your project:
#   - Routes API              (turn-by-turn directions)
#   - Maps Static API         (minimap image)
#   - Geocoding API           (address → lat/lng)
#   - Places API              (autocomplete in phone UI)
#   - Roads API               (speed limits — requires Asset Tracking license)
#
# Speed limit note:
#   The Roads API speedLimits endpoint requires a Google Maps Asset Tracking
#   license. Without it, nearestRoads still works but speedLimits returns 403.
#   The app handles this gracefully — the speed limit badge is hidden and
#   everything else continues normally.
#   Asset Tracking pricing: https://mapsplatform.google.com/pricing/

VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_KEY=YOUR_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY_HERE
